        "subject": "LU-18925 build: 64k client do not use pgidx before defined",
        "message": "LU-18925 build: 64k client do not use pgidx before defined\n\nBuild fix for 64k\n\ndt_object.c:1034:53: error: 'pgidx' undeclared \\\n   (first use in this function); did you mean 'pid'?\n 1034 |                 void *kaddr = kmap_local_page(pages[pgidx]);\n      |                                                     ^~~~~\n      |                                                     pid\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: ea0bdfc7cf0 (\"LU-18925 libcfs: prefer kmap_local_page\")\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I359b3a927b2360d327da6dd7d7a6b92c9f2281d5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60431\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey.lyashkov@hpe.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\n"
